Invocation Name: interesting facts
des:
Ask for Interesting Facts, and learn about some really amazing facts.

Interesting Facts provides fun the whole family can enjoy and is guaranteed to make you smarter.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Interesting Facts" or "Alexa, open Interesting Facts" to get a fact".

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
